  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the efficacy, safety, and tolerability of sofosbuvir /velpatasvir
      (SOF/VEL) fixed dose combination (FDC) and SOF/VEL FDC and Ribavirin (RBV) for 12 weeks in
      participants with chronic genotype 3 HCV infection and compensated cirrhosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
